is not a motivated person.

169
00:08:24,546 --> 00:08:27,757
Also, if you look at the fourth toes,

170
00:08:27,841 --> 00:08:29,551
they're asymmetrical.

171
00:08:30,301 --> 00:08:32,762
One is too small,
and the other is too big.

172
00:08:34,556 --> 00:08:37,475
This could mean financial problems.

173
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,768
Oh, so he can see that too.

174
00:08:39,728 --> 00:08:42,939
So I say with certainty

175
00:08:43,982 --> 00:08:45,025
that number 4 is the answer.

176
00:08:45,108 --> 00:08:46,526
KIM BAEKMUN CHOSE NUMBER 4

177
00:08:46,609 --> 00:08:48,194
That's so cool. He said, "with certainty."

178
00:08:49,529 --> 00:08:51,322
- He said, "with certainty."
- "With certainty."

179
00:08:51,823 --> 00:08:54,075
- Number 4. He's not even perplexed.
- He's certain.

180
00:08:55,285 --> 00:08:57,912
His answer was the same as mine.

181
00:08:57,996 --> 00:09:00,290
I thought, "Oh, I got it right."

182
00:09:00,373 --> 00:09:01,624
I felt relieved.

183
00:09:03,209 --> 00:09:05,670
Next, Taeul Lee Dokyu.

184
00:09:06,421 --> 00:09:08,131
The face reader.

185
00:09:08,214 --> 00:09:09,215
The face reader.

186
00:09:09,299 --> 00:09:12,385
I've studied a bit of podiatry before.

187
00:09:12,469 --> 00:09:15,513
The shape of feet number 9
is quite unusual.

188
00:09:17,974 --> 00:09:19,934
Oh, so podiatry is a thing.

189
00:09:20,894 --> 00:09:21,978
Oh…

190
00:09:22,062 --> 00:09:26,107
They also have tetanus scars,
which are often found on homeless people,

191
00:09:26,191 --> 00:09:29,903
and the brain lines
on the big toes are crooked.

192
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:33,323
So you can tell such things
by looking at the toes.

193
00:09:34,115 --> 00:09:37,660
They didn't look like
an ordinary pair of feet,

194
00:09:37,744 --> 00:09:38,912
so I chose number 9.

195
00:09:38,995 --> 00:09:43,875
TAEUL LEE DOKYU CHOSE NUMBER 9

196
00:09:45,293 --> 00:09:46,753
Next, Monad.

197
00:09:47,462 --> 00:09:49,380
Wow…

198
00:09:49,464 --> 00:09:51,174
Her presence is no joke.

199
00:09:51,758 --> 00:09:53,843
With that curly blonde hair.

200
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:57,597
The moment I heard "homeless,"

201
00:09:57,680 --> 00:10:01,184
the first thing I thought was "no home."

202
00:10:01,851 --> 00:10:03,436
Homeless people have no homes.

203
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,647
Right. No place of residence.

204
00:10:05,730 --> 00:10:07,774
Except for number 4,

205
00:10:07,857 --> 00:10:11,111
