214
00:10:41,683 --> 00:10:43,601
Their home is where they are,

215
00:10:43,685 --> 00:10:46,104
and they don't have a fixed address.

216
00:10:46,187 --> 00:10:49,357
I think number 4 is homeless.

217
00:10:50,358 --> 00:10:51,526
That's so intriguing.

218
00:10:51,609 --> 00:10:53,361
I got the Wanderer card too.

219
00:10:53,444 --> 00:10:55,446
Our cards are exactly the same.

220
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:57,991
- How do you get that with tarot?
- How did she get that?

221
00:10:58,074 --> 00:10:59,325
Most of them said 4.

222
00:10:59,409 --> 00:11:00,702
Oh…

223
00:11:01,369 --> 00:11:03,413
