224
00:11:04,789 --> 00:11:05,790
The survivor is…

225
00:11:07,250 --> 00:11:08,835
I want to make it.

226
00:11:08,918 --> 00:11:12,046
It's not my area of expertise,
but I'd still like to win.

227
00:11:12,881 --> 00:11:14,340
I wanted to advance.

228
00:11:14,424 --> 00:11:17,927
