229
00:11:18,011 --> 00:11:21,931
I was worried I might not
get this because it'd be a bad look.

230
00:11:22,015 --> 00:11:25,852
To be honest,
I was pretty confident.

231
00:11:27,395 --> 00:11:28,396
The survivor is

232
00:11:29,689 --> 00:11:30,940
Hong Yuljae.

233
00:11:32,483 --> 00:11:33,484
Whoo!

234
00:11:33,568 --> 00:11:34,569
HONG YULJAE SURVIVES

235
00:11:34,652 --> 00:11:35,820
See? Number 4.

236
00:11:35,904 --> 00:11:38,615
Number 4. That was the answer.

237
00:11:38,698 --> 00:11:40,450
Whoa, what a shaman.

238
00:11:41,492 --> 00:11:43,369
I feel bad for Mr. Kim.

239
00:11:43,453 --> 00:11:44,454
Me too.

240
00:11:44,537 --> 00:11:46,873
Kim Baekmun and Monad

241
00:11:46,956 --> 00:11:48,708
