242
00:11:48,791 --> 00:11:52,086
but Hong Yuljae survives as he went first.

243
00:11:52,170 --> 00:11:53,421
So close.

244
00:11:54,339 --> 00:11:55,381
The fourth pair of feet

245
00:11:55,465 --> 00:11:57,634
belongs to Son,

246
00:11:57,717 --> 00:12:00,220
who has been living on the streets,

247
00:12:00,303 --> 00:12:02,222
