251
00:12:07,644 --> 00:12:09,270
How do you figure out things like that?

252
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:15,151
Hong Yuljae was the first person
to choose number 4.

253
00:12:15,235 --> 00:12:16,778
Can you explain in detail

254
00:12:16,861 --> 00:12:18,279
