an organ near the ribs cut out.

1284
01:02:34,459 --> 01:02:37,045
- Ooh! An organ.
- Whoa.

1285
01:02:39,339 --> 01:02:40,674
That's so accurate.

1286
01:02:42,050 --> 01:02:44,761
He also had trouble breathing.

1287
01:02:45,971 --> 01:02:46,972
And I keep…

1288
01:02:48,306 --> 01:02:51,518
I keep feeling nauseous.

1289
01:02:51,601 --> 01:02:53,269
-That's crazy. Nausea.
-Yes.

1290
01:02:53,353 --> 01:02:54,896
It's crazy she guessed
stomach issues right.

1291
01:02:55,814 --> 01:02:59,943
People in his family
must watch their brain and heart health

1292
01:03:00,026 --> 01:03:01,319
and be careful on the road.

1293
01:03:01,403 --> 01:03:02,862
It just keeps coming out.

1294
01:03:02,946 --> 01:03:06,491
I can't just say 2 things,
but if I must choose…

1295
01:03:08,368 --> 01:03:09,494
Brain and heart.

1296
01:03:09,577 --> 01:03:14,958
INEUIDANG
BRAIN & HEART

1297
01:03:15,041 --> 01:03:17,085
All readings have been shared.

1298
01:03:17,794 --> 01:03:22,257
Fate Reapers, please pick the person
who read the fate

1299
01:03:23,174 --> 01:03:25,427
most accurately.

1300
01:03:26,302 --> 01:03:27,846
What should we do?

1301
01:03:28,430 --> 01:03:30,056
This is tough.

1302
01:03:30,765 --> 01:03:34,102
We should go with this person.

1303
01:03:34,185 --> 01:03:35,854
- Lee Sobin?
- Yes, her.

1304
01:03:35,937 --> 01:03:38,314
"His stomach was cut."

1305
01:03:38,398 --> 01:03:40,233
A tube in his neck.

1306
01:03:40,316 --> 01:03:43,486
But it was Ineuidang
who got the details right.

1307
01:03:43,570 --> 01:03:46,656
She spoke as if she saw his X-ray scans.

1308
01:03:46,740 --> 01:03:48,241
- She said she felt nauseous.
- Yes.

1309
01:03:48,324 --> 01:03:50,869
- It says she feels nauseous.
- Even now.

1310
01:03:50,952 --> 01:03:53,538
Right, we should pick 1 of the 2.

1311
01:03:53,621 --> 01:03:54,914
It's hard to choose.

1312
01:03:58,126 --> 01:04:01,087
Let me announce the Fate Reapers' choice.

1313
01:04:02,547 --> 01:04:06,009
I said what I saw as soon as he walked in.

1314
01:04:06,092 --> 01:04:07,802
I just decided to trust my deities.

1315
01:04:08,511 --> 01:04:10,430
My deities told me,

1316
01:04:10,513 --> 01:04:12,307
"Don't worry, you're in the top tier."

1317
01:04:12,807 --> 01:04:15,226
The survivor who guessed correctly…

1318
01:04:19,564 --> 01:04:21,483
is…

1319
01:05:18,498 --> 01:05:20,500
Translated by Jennifer Jean Lim
